# TITLE: 3D Printed Ear Phone Case

This project was created in my Engineering Design Class in February 2025 individually as a creative way to design this everyday item people use in modern day.

## OBJECTIVE: I can design a 3-D printed protective case that can serve customer personal needs, improve their lifestyles, and make the design look visually 
pleasing so that others can buy it.

## PROJECT OVERVIEW: Contains the documentation that has the solution rationale, design statement, concept sketches, solution path, anotated concept sketch with 
tolerances, working drawings in multiview, photo of 3D printed model, and reflection. 

## TECHNOLOGIES USED: WORD Document (REDESIGN OF PROTECTIVE CASE PROJECT BY ROHAN RAMANATHAN) and FUSION 360.

## USAGE: Open As Word Document and 3D Design in Fusion 360.
